    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p><span class="lead">Standing Orders of the Court of Queen Margaret University </span></p>
<div class="page">
<div class="layoutArea">
<div class="column">
<p>These standing orders are supplementary to The Queen Margaret University, Edinburgh (Scotland) Order of Council 2007 (Scottish Statutory Instrument No. 2007/116) (“the Order of Council”), and The Queen Margaret University Edinburgh (Scotland) Amendment Order of Council 2019, and shall be interpreted in accordance there with.</p>
</div>
